---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../lib/site";
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  lede="Short version: we collect almost nothing, and we don't sell any of it."
>
  <p><em>Last updated: July 2026. This is a starting template — have it reviewed before treating it as legal compliance.</em></p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>Newsletter:</strong> your email address, when you give it to us.
    It's stored with our newsletter provider and used to send you the
    newsletter. Nothing else.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Analytics:</strong> we use privacy-respecting, cookieless analytics
    that collect aggregate usage data (pages visited, referrers, country-level
    location). No personal profiles, no cross-site tracking, no advertising
    identifiers.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Story pitches:</strong> what you submit through the pitch form is
    used to evaluate and follow up on your pitch, and for nothing else.
  </p>

  <h2>What we don't do</h2>
  <p>
    We don't sell or rent your data, we don't run third-party advertising
    trackers, and we don't share your email with sponsors.
  </p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <p>
    Every newsletter has a one-click unsubscribe. To have your data deleted —
    email address, pitch submissions, anything — write to
    <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a> and we'll
    confirm when it's done.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
